| 14 | Developer scripts (start-core.sh, stop-core.sh) | 2 | | #3 | Scripts bring up & tear down dependencies locally |
| 15 | Architecture README initial draft (E-Com + infra) | 2 | | #1-#6 | README includes sequence diagram text |

